    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a champ for me. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road, this is the one! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. It retains the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance is extensive, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis integrity is secured with documented subframe reinforcement. Equipped with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, the turn-in is precise with minimal body roll. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp. A driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance records available. Minor interior wear. Engine runs well. Tires are recent.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
