      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit is mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission, providing a direct mechanical connection often lost in modern dual-clutch setups. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring optimal lateral grip and torque vectoring. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle body actuator servicing. The Alpine White exterior remains sharp, and the Novillo leather interior shows only minor bolster wear. No subframe fatigue or VANOS noise. This is a mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the canyons.",
